Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.00,Default,opsync,0,0,0,,{opsync}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:47.33,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,The targets are approaching the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.27,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.17,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,The two in the back sound like heavyweights{/bodyguards/muscle}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.20,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,They're avoiding all windows and doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:57.33,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Judging by their movements, \Nthey're definitely pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:06.20,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Conrad is sitting on the sofa next to the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:09.05,Default,Conrad,0,0,0,,All right, let's see what you've brought for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.50,Default,Conrad,0,0,0,,You'll get your payment after.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.36,Default,A,0,0,0,,Y-You better hold up your end of the deal. {c: does something like "I hope you hold up your end of the deal" work} {K: that works}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:21.15,Default,Conrad,0,0,0,,This is, without a doubt, the data \NI've been looking for. All right, as promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:22.57,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,The deal is underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.38,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,All right, we're heading in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:25.67,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.21,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.23,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,We're with the State Security Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.02,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,You're all being detained under the suspicion \Nof being spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.59,Default,Conrad,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:50.78,Default,Conrad,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:56.70,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hello there, you traitorous scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.70,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,We have a wonderful cell \Nwith your name on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.59,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,so please accompany us \Nto the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.71,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Excellent work, Second Lieutenant Briar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.54,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.89,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,We need you to take care \Nof this fellow next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:19.36,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Have you heard about the various \Nbooks and articles going around
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.25,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,in the West that mock and slander Ostania?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:26.64,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,It's nothing but bold-faced lies \Nand conspiracy theories. {K: what are "base lies"? literal is just "fabricated stories/made-up shit (and conspiracy theories)"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.91,Default,Boss,0,0,130,,A lot of them are made by shady printing presses\Nhere in Ostania
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.72,Default,Boss,0,0,130,,and are sold to the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:38.19,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,And among the writers, this guy popped up. {K: consider "this guy" for the こいつ nuance}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.74,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Franklin Perkin. Age 39.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:45.34,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,He was a journalist \Nduring the previous administration,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:48.88,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,and was arrested \Nfor aiding anti-government extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.71,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,I want you to follow him \Nand get the evidence we need,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.13,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,along with the names of whoever buys\Nhis propaganda. {K: i prefer "names of his buyers" or a similar wording here; he doesn't care about the readers themselves, he's looking for whoever is distributing penkin's work in the west}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.08,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,As ridiculous as these articles are,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.76,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,there are plenty of idiots in \Nthe West who'll believe them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.97,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,I want him dealt with \Nbefore this reaches public consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.14,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.35,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,Aren't we working Yuri a bit too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:08.64,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'll be just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.65,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Selling out your own country\Nto make a quick buck...{Showing contempt for your own \Ncountry for chump change...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:17.78,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Just the fact that my sister\Nbreathes the same air as this scum...{I can't even stand the thought of \Nthis filth breathing the same air}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:20.14,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,is all the motivation I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:27.55,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8}Observation of subject \NJ-095: Franklin Perkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.41,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}On the 6th, subject wakes at 07:21.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.50,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Subject watches the television \Nprogram {\i0}Good Morning Ostania{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.17,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Subject curses at the newscaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:41.18,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}08:10, subject leaves \Nfor job at the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.76,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}See appendices for details of his attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.82,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Subject rides on third car of the U-8 train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.65,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}See appendices for descriptions \Nof fellow passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:02.05,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}At 12:06, subject goes to the \Nrestaurant Fjord with coworker M.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.75,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Orders lunch Set A.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.66,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}See appendices for log \Nof conversation topics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.97,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}At 17:49, subject leaves work \Nand goes to central market.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.29,Default,TV Reporter,0,0,0,,{\i1}At noon today,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:25.68,Default,TV Reporter,0,0,0,,{\i1}the 12th Annual International Education \NSymposium was held in Frejis.
Comment: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:29.05,Default,Vincent,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sonia... were you deceiving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:29.05,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}At 18:33, subject returns home
Comment: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:34.17,Default,Sonia,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no! You're the only one I love, Vincent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:33.19,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}and watches television programs \N{\i0}News 20{\i1} and {\i0}Berlint in Love{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:35.42,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Subject appears infatuated \Nwith the female lead.
Comment: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.42,Default,Vincent,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then why—
Comment: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.69,Default,Sonia,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}To prove my love—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:39.90,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}No further noteworthy activities \Nbefore retiring for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.75,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,You sure didn't hold back on the details. {K: this is a "you sure put in a fuckton of effort into spying on this guy" rather than a "this is an awfully detailed report". line might be fine as is, though}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.25,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:49.68,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,You've been doing this for two days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.71,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,You should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.43,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.96,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Here's my next report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.46,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,"On the 7th, at 08:07, \Nsubject goes to work."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.96,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,"Has lunch at the restaurant \NFjord and orders lunch Set B..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:08.73,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,"Fjord."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.08,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,"Yor."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.76,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,You're clearly tired. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.59,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,No. That always happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:25.17,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Open up, Mr. Perkin! I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:35.09,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,H-Hey there, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.75,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,How many times do I need \Nto tell you to pay your rent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.57,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Could I just have a bit more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.76,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,That's what you told me last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:48.51,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,All right then, two more days!\NI promise I'll get it to you by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.29,Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,This is your last chance.\NNext time, you're getting evicted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.37,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Stupid landlady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.24,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Heading out for a bit, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.92,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,There's some leftover food here if you get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.89,Default,Perkin's Father,0,0,0,,All right. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.27,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Does he think he's being followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:23.81,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,That, or he's looking for something to write about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:34.54,Default,Politician,0,0,0,,Our country must face this with resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:35.31,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.14,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,Let's teach the West a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.14,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Not a single good story in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:13.40,Default,Child A,0,0,0,,Check out this cool Bondman pistol I got!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:17.10,Default,Child B,0,0,0,,No way! Can I give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.48,Default,Child A,0,0,0,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.83,Default,Child C,0,0,0,,Meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.11,Default,Child A,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.54,Default,Child A,0,0,0,,My pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:40.78,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Overcome by poverty, street children \Ndesperately dig through trash for scraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.88,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.92,Default,Child A,0,0,0,,What the heck is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.31,Default,Child B,0,0,0,,We're gonna tell the Secret Police on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:53.67,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Listen closely, \Nyou greedy little upper-class snot-nosed brat. {K: prefer more of a "spoiled (i.e. rich, middle-class) brat" nuance here, but this is fine}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.73,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,People whose ideals lean toward \Nthe West, like yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.48,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,are the ones who are going to get arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.23,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.82,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:04.19,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm gonna execute him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:04.19,Alt,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:10.20,Default,First Lieutenant,0,0,0,,First, we need to find out\Nwho's buying his underground publications.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:23.54,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,They're going to love this one!{This article should make some people laugh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.97,Default,Perkin's Father,0,0,0,,Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.74,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:37.55,Default,Perkin's Father,0,0,0,,You haven't gotten involved\Nwith the wrong people again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.47,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,I-I haven't. Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:43.93,Default,Perkin's Father,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for your odd sense of justice, {K: i'm not sure about "odd" here, all he's saying really is that it was unnecessary. consider "If it wasn't for your strong sense of justice,"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:47.47,Default,Perkin's Father,0,0,0,,you could've kept your job at the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:59.46,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,What's so wrong about trying to improve \Nthe lives of the people I love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:07.75,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Even now, we scrimp and save\Njust to keep living paycheck to paycheck. {we need money just to \Nkeep up this lousy living situation.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.31,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,If we had money, Mom would've...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.92,Default,Perkin's Father,0,0,0,,Hey, Frank...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.76,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Just forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:53.30,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}On the 11th at 08:36, \Nsubject leaves for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:09.05,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's had no interactions so far\Nthat would give us a lead on his buyers.
Comment: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:09.05,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}that would connect him with one of his buyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.57,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.23,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}he does it at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.58,Default,Postal worker,0,0,0,,Here's all the mail that's been inspected!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.03,Default,Postal worker,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.08,Default,Joseph,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:29.59,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,I'll take care of those, Joseph. \NGo ahead and get some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.34,Default,Joseph,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks! {39}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.41,Default,Joseph,0,0,0,,What should I have today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.87,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he's been slipping them in\Nafter they've passed inspection.{flag}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:06.62,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:09.66,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}you won't like what happens next. {K: literal is "you won't have any room for excuses", i think that's why the original went with "talk your way out". this change seems fine to me though}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.68,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}On the 15th at 08:02.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.98,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,I'm heading to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:33.95,Default,Perkin's Father,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.92,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,The State Security... Service.{THE FEDS? YO THE FEDS ARE HERE}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:05.04,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Sorry, Dad. I might not be back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.94,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Franklin Perkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:19.06,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I believe you're the one who wrote this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:26.10,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,We've already arrested the buyer\Nthis was addressed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.33,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.11,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,I appreciate you waiting outside for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.58,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Who knew State Security officers \Ncould be so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:37.59,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,It's so your family doesn't have \Nto see how much of a lowlife you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.42,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:47.14,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,I'm trying to fight a corrupt government,\Nwhile you serve as its lapdog.{The one who fought a corrupt government, \Nor the one who served it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.60,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,Who's actually the lowlife here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.36,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I would never do anything \Nto cause my family concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:59.61,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:12.25,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'll request that your father \Nreceive some financial aid to get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:22.97,Default,Perkin,0,0,0,,I appreciate it. {K: consider changing to "i appreciate it" or similar; imo he should sound more grateful}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.27,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Hello there, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.68,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.80,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,You've been working hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.00,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,I'm happy to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.40,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm honored, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:43.15,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,This must be rather difficult work for a newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.31,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Don't let the stress build up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:46.91,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:50.41,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I think I'm quite well-suited for this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:56.00,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'll use this momentum to capture Twilight \Nand protect the peace of this nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.88,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,Well, that'd be just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:05.05,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll treat you \Nto one of my favorite meat places. {K: could shorten this maybe? literal is just "I'll treat you to some (really) good meat sometime." idk how to make it more natural tho}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.73,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Really?! I'm gonna hold you to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.94,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.30,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hiya, Yor{Sis}!{c: capitalized Sis is evil}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.70,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Yuri? What are you doing here\Nso late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.00,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Unkie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.44,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Good evening, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.70,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you here, Forger?! \NPick up a night shift, or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.45,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.38,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,I was just feeling a bit homesick, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.22,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Why are you pestering me, pooch?{What do you want, stupid leash girl?}{c: how to make this not sound terrible}{K: no idea :poppo:}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:57.23,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've had a long day at work, \Nso why don't I make us some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:05.09,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yor, Yor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:10.24,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yor, Yor, Yor, Yor, Yor, Yor, Yor, Yor, Yor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.98,Default,Yuri,0,0,0,,Yor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:14.88,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:18.23,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,We're going to get a noise complaint\Nif you don't calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.68,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}My name is Bondman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.56,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}I'll take it from here.\NYou go on ahead, Agent M!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.69,Default,Agent M,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.58,Default,Agent M,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}I don't want to lose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:49.97,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}M...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.70,Default,Agent M,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}I'll do whatever it takes \Nto stay with you, Bondman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.78,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Time to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.92,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}My spotless suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:00.21,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}My beloved, gleaming silver car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:03.71,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}The techniques I mastered through countless \Nbattles, and my gentlemanly demeanor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.71,Default,Agent M,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Oh, you're such a masterful driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.22,Default,Agent M,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}I love you, Bondman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:15.47,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Since I'm the coolest and so clever,\N romance comes naturally.{it's this easy}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:18.73,Default,Enemy spy,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}My country has been at odds with yours\Nfor as long as I can remember.{I work as a spy in a country \Nyou consider an enemy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.73,Default,Enemy spy,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}If you keep getting in my way,\N I won't show you mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.72,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}How fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:29.82,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}We're all just humans\Ntrying to live on the same planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.89,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Why do we need to fight over \Nsomething as petty as a line on a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:36.83,Default,Enemy spy,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Then why don't you stop this conflict?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.12,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}The peace treaty has been signed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.90,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}The boundaries that once separated us \Nare no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:48.84,Default,Enemy spy,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}You're amazing, Bondman! \NI'll never let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:53.48,Default,Gina,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}My father's obsessed with \Ncreating this Destroyer Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.27,Default,Gina,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Please stop him, Bondman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.85,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}But of course, Gina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.97,Default,Gina,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Oh, thank you so much, Bondman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.75,Default,Gina,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Once my father wakes up, \NI'd love to introduce you to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.86,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}I'd love to, Gina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:10.25,Default,Terrorist Woman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}My terrorist boyfriend{lover}\N was arrested because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.88,Default,Terrorist Woman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:16.87,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Revenge won't relieve your pain,\Nbut I believe my love just might.
Comment: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.87,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}I'll save you with the power of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:21.85,Default,Female Director,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}We won't stop until we've taken over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.88,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Never mind all that. Let's go out on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:32.13,Default,Landlady 2,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Hello, Bondman.\N I'm here to collect this month's rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:35.18,Default,Landlady 2,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Also, there are noise complaints \Nfrom the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.37,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Well, hello there! \NYou're looking as beautiful as ever, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.80,Default,Agent M,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Hey! What's with all these broads?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:49.69,Default,Terrorist Woman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Pick one already, damn it!
Comment: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.02,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.34,Default,Enemy Spy,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}How many of us are you dating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.45,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}You cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:56.66,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,{\c&H00D2FF&\fnArial\b1\fscx92.7\fscy90}I'm going to make every last \Nlady in this world happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.10,Default,Bondman,0,0,0,,Dealing with risk is just a part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:16.97,Default,TV Narrator,0,0,0,,Next time on {\i1}Spy Wars{\i0}: "Bondman Returns!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:20.18,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,This must be one of those flirting stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.20,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Now I can talk with Becky about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.34,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I think I've become a real grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.49,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:29.50,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}How was anything he did gentlemanly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.94,Default,edsync,0,0,0,,{edsync}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.51,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna ride the panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:17.07,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot comprehend the appeal\Nof riding these ever-popular pandas.
Comment: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.07,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}riding this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:19.64,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do children insist on riding this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:21.79,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's slow and extremely boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:25.66,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus, it feels like deliberate government \Nbrainwashing intended to null the brain
Comment: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:26.77,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}to steal the emotions of the passenger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:28.81,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}of the passenger \Nmaking them an unwavering puppet of their—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:33.17,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna ride it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.81,Alt,Yor,0,0,0,,Let's let her ride it, Loid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:47.83,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Was that fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.84,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna ride it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:52.58,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:22:00.09,Default,TV Announcer,0,0,0,,The Silt Seashore is where people go \Nto make the most of their summer!{The Silt Seashore is packed with people \Nwanting to enjoy various seaside activities.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:02.73,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I wanna go to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.58,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Well, we can't go to the beach, \Nbut we {\i1}can{\i0} go to a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:13.11,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:18.25,Default,Yor,0,0,0,,I'm so glad she's enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:25.56,Default,Child 1,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Oops, I just peed a little. \NNot like anyone's going to find out, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:27.12,Default,Child 2,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I feel so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:32.31,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,I'm never going in a pool again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:35.48,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! But it looked like she was enjoying herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:37.08,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't understand children.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:53.27,Default,Ewen,0,0,0,,Time to get up, Lord Damian.\NYou don't wanna miss roll call again, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:54.35,Default,Ewen,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:58.31,Default,Emil,0,0,0,,Lord Damian!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.73,Default,Ewen,0,0,0,,You were already awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:03.03,Default,Damian,0,0,0,,Yeah, about an hour ago. \NI was reviewing my notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.68,Default,Damian,0,0,0,,It's pretty rare that I oversleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:08.03,Default,Ewen,0,0,0,,Impressive as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:13.48,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Wake up, Anya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:16.64,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,You've only got ten minutes \Nuntil your bus gets here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:18.99,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Anya has ten more minutes \Nuntil the explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.99,0:23:20.56,Default,Anya,0,0,0,,Anya will stop it...{she's got this}{so true}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:22.55,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:26.63,Default,Loid,0,0,0,,We can't afford another Tonitrus Bolt!
